{"tid":2161603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10.1屯門衝突 片段顯示男生被搜身前警員已手持證物 辯方質疑警方插贓","createTime":"2020-08-17T15:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T18:10:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f510a319ac3eca1ba671d968027e52cea98281cc","tid":2161603,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/ZEBBMXU2EBGF3CEOPZICJV6YTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FZEBBMXU2EBGF3CEOPZICJV6YTA%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21L3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=c212ea4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FZEBBMXU2EBGF3CEOPZICJV6YTA%2F&h=8c6d7b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/ZEBBMXU2EBGF3CEOPZICJV6YTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10.1當天全港多區爆發衝突，多人被捕。其中三名男女於屯門被捕，被控非法集結等罪。案件今在屯門法院開審，辯方指現場片段顯示，首被告被警方搜身前，已有軍裝警手持涉案行山杖。拘捕首被告的警員看片後同意說法，直言不清楚為何會有此事，亦承認制服首被告至搜身之間，相隔了20至30分鐘，其間不知同袍有否接觸過該行山杖，惟他不同意辯方所指，他或同袍在附近拾獲涉案行山杖，再放進首被告的背囊插贓。"},{"pid":"68b726cef4faeaf63490cba145c96bc83fd9d1c5","tid":2161603,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8427c11c1de525fb50fc1e050737e5ed10618ba9","tid":2161603,"uid":291448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（YouTube戰線）集一眾連登網軍之力 睇下今年之內可唔可以幫呢個黃營頻道突破十萬訂閱？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161547</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8760b62d28157d280822c93a3d905656b9d520db","tid":2161603,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"